snippet.title: New Super Lucky's Tale Trailer
snippet.description: #NewSuperLuckysTale launches today on Xbox One and Xbox GamePass! Join Lucky on his quest to rescue the Book of Ages from the mysterious Jinx and his Kitty Litter in this delightful 3D platforming adventure.
